Introduction

Evie, formerly known as May is a Thai singer formely under Big Ocean ENM. She was a member of the upcoming girl group iii. She is best known for participating in the survival show Universe Ticket, where she was eliminated in the 4th episode.

She seems to have left Big Ocean ENM and iii sometime in early to mid-2024.
